"``[\"LICENSE.txt\", \"_vendor/packaging/LICENSE*\"]`` as glob patterns, or "
"``[\"LICENSE.txt\", \"_vendor/LICENSE-APACHE.txt\", \"_vendor/LICENSE-BSD."
