#: ../source/specifications/pyproject-toml.rst:448
msgid ""
"Corresponding :ref:`core metadata <core-metadata>` field: :ref:`Requires-"
"Dist <core-metadata-requires-dist>` and :ref:`Provides-Extra <core-metadata-"
"provides-extra>`"
